<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=1106" title="Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince arrives"> Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince arrives</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>Darlene just got an email that the new Harry Potter book had shipped. &#8220;Shoot, I guess that means I won&#8217;t get it today. Oh, who knows maybe they&#8217;ll deliver it later. You can always hope.&#8221;</p>

	<p>Well, not 10 minutes later, I hear a light knock on the door. I had to scramble to get downstairs. The mailman was already down the street, but I managed to catch him.</p>

	<p>Of course, he hands me a box labeled &#8220;Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince.&#8221;</p>

	<p>I now have a happy potter reading Harry Potter&#8230;</p>



 
<div class="line"></div>

<div class="smallcat">Posted in <a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?c=Life">Life</a></div>
