<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=1089" title="A email from a friend"> A email from a friend</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p><blockquote>Did I tell you about the scare I had over my cat recently? She&#8217;d gotten out and I thought she&#8217;d gotten pregnant, but as it turns out, she had merely eaten a whole ball of yarn. And then she had mittens.</blockquote></p>

	<p>I could only wish to be this good at puns. He had me hook, line and sinker.</p>



 
